quran[46]{c,v,t}:
  79,1,"Ibut ko di-i Nggagandur to­mukao (a manga Malaikat),"
  79,2,"Go so Puphamanonggos sa mananai,"
  79,3,"Go so Puphamanoron sa maga-an,"
  79,4,"Go so Puphamangonakona mona,"
  79,5,"Go so gi-i Thatandingan ko Sogowan (ka Pagoyagun kano dun);"
  79,6,"Si-i ko Alongan a Thambu­tambug so Phakatambug,"
  79,7,"A matondog sukaniyan o pha­katondog."
  79,8,"So manga poso sa Alongan noto na ma-aluk,"
  79,9,"So manga kailai ron na Maka­susunong."
  79,10,"Gi-i ran Tharo-on: Ba Mata­-an! A sukutano na khikasoi tano dun ko asal a butad (a kaoya­goyag)?"
  79,11,"Ati apiya pun mabaloi tano a manga tolan a miyanga rorophod?"
  79,12,"Pitharo iran: A giyoto man na sa maoto na kapakakasoi a kalogi!"
  79,13,"Na giyoto na Satiman bo a Lalis,"
  79,14,"Na sa maoto na siran na matago siran ko liyawao o Lopa (a manga Oyagoyag)."
  79,15,"Ino a Miyakatalingoma Ruka so Totholan ko Musa?"
  79,16,"Gowani a itawag Rukaniyan o Kadnan Niyan si-i ko balintad a Soti a giya Towa:"
  79,17,"Songka ko Pir-aon, -Mata­ an! A sukaniyan na Miyangakowa­la,-"
  79,18,"Na Tharowangka: Ino kha­baya ka a Masoti ka?"
  79,19,"Go Manggonanao Akun suka ko Kadnan ka, na Makapananggi­laka."
  79,20,"Na Piyaki-ilai Niyan non so tanda a mala."
  79,21,"Na Piyakambokhag iyan go Somiyangka,"
  79,22,"Oriyan niyan na Tomiyali­khod a gi-i nggaga-an,"
  79,23,"Na tominimo sa tao go Piya­kalangkap iyan,"
  79,24,"Sa Pitharo iyan: Sakun i To­han niyo a Maporo."
  79,25,"Na ini danugon o Allah so siksa ko Mori, a go so Paganai."
  79,26,"Mata-an! A adun a matatago saya a titho a Thoma ko tao a Ma­alukun (ko Allah)."
  79,27,"Ba sukano i marugun a adu­nun, antawaa so Langit? Pimbalai Niyan Sukaniyan:"
  79,28,"Ini Poro lyan so kaporo iyan, go Pithaong lyan Phiyapiya,"
  79,29,"Go Piyakalibotung Iyan so gagawi-i ron, go Piyakaliwanag lyan so daondao ron;"
  79,30,"Go so Lopa ko oriyan noto na Kiyayat Iyan,"
  79,31,"Piyakambowat lyan non so ig rukaniyan, a go so manga Pangu­nungkun non;"
  79,32,"Go so manga Palao na Piya­makabukun Niyan non,"
  79,33,"Pagupur rukano a go so man­ga Ayam miyo."
  79,34,"Na amai ka Makatalingoma so khaolaola a mala,"
  79,35,"Si-i ko Alongan a Katadu­man o Manosiya so Pinggolaola niyan,"
  79,36,"Go payagun so Naraka Jahim ko phakailai ron."
  79,37,"Na so puman so tao a Miyan­gakowala,"
  79,38,"Go miyatomo iyan so kaoya­ goyag sa doniya,"
  79,39,"Na Mata-an! A so Naraka Jahim na giyoto i darpa iyan."
  79,40,"Na so puman so miyaluk sa ka Kha-adapa niyan ko Kadnan Niyan, go pininggun niyan a ginawa niyan ko kabaya a ribat."
  79,41,"Na Mata-an! A so Sorga na giyoto i darpa iyan."
  79,42,"lpagisha iran Ruka so Bang­kit, o andai kaphakadongko iyan?"
  79,43,"Na Bangka kiran noto Ka­phakisaboti?"
  79,44,"Si-i bo ko Kadnan Ka so Khadansalan niyan."
  79,45,"Mata-an! A Suka na matag Ka Phamaka-iktiyar ko ma-aluk Rukaniyan."
  79,46,"Lagid o ba Mata-an a siran ko Alongan a kasandungi ranon na da-a minitarug iran (ko doniya) a rowar ko kagabi gabi o di na so kapita pita!"
